.TH PRODBOX_rke2 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-rke2 \- Local cluster lifecycle
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox rke2
.SH DESCRIPTION
Local cluster lifecycle commands.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBstatus\fR
Check RKE2 status
.TP
\fBstart\fR
Start RKE2
.TP
\fBstop\fR
Stop RKE2
.TP
\fBrestart\fR
Restart RKE2
.TP
\fBreconcile\fR
Reconcile RKE2
.TP
\fBdelete\fR
Delete RKE2
.TP
\fBlogs\fR
Show RKE2 logs
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox rke2 reconcile\fR
Reconcile the supported local cluster state.
